Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,People or heirlooms?{人が大事か家宝が大事か}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the question - or so Shakespeare would say.{そこが問題とセイクスペアなら言うけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The count is furious{怒りに怒った老伯爵は}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After vowing to split her open,{刀のサビにしてくれよ 立て迫り来る}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, who calculated the timing, intervened and stopped the count,{タイミングを見計らった少尉の再確でこと なきを得たものの}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but Benio was already determined to leave the house.{こんな家にはもうおさらばと 自ら産んでる羽目となる}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For once, the count's stubbornness{一方 伯爵家では}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was not approved by the other family members.{老伯爵の頑固も多数決の世論には更新がなく}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Shinobu decided to go look for Benio.{少尉が呼び戻しの使者に立つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I dispatch.{それでは行ってまいります}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a problem-{だがしかしどっこい}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Her father is just as strict!{厳しい父親が言おうとは}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand why I brough this here?{ここれを何のために持たせたと思っとる}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is deplorable! I feel so sorry to the Sublieutenant!{情けない伊集院君に申し訳がない}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say that{言わせてもらいますけどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.05,0:02:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it is Shinobu who is deplorable!{情けないのは 伊集院少尉の方なんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise that womaniser!{あんな女ったらし大嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Womaniser?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He has this many love letters every day,{毎日毎日こんなにラブレターの舞い込むし}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,also he's in really close to a geisha from Yaginabashi.{それに仲のいい柳橋の芸者さんだとか}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A geisha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And sadly, on top of that, she's a bit prettier than me!{ええ、それにね、悔しいけど私よりちょびっと美人}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that he'd do such things...{むぅ、まさかあの男に限ってそんなことはあるまい}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you trust my words, Father?{お父様は私の言うこと信じないんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!{黙れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way an imperial soldier would do such indecent things!{帝国軍人がそのようないかがわしいことをする筈がない}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldier here and soldier there,{軍人、軍人って言いますけどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,are soldiers such admirable people?{そんなに軍人は立派な人間なんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hit the table!{机を叩くんじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one doing that!?{叩いているのはそっちじゃないですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up!{黙れ黙れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you affronting soldiers!?{軍人を侮辱するか}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You just trust others more than your own daughter!{大体自分の娘より他人を信じるなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!{黙れ黙れ黙れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like father, like daughter...{やっぱり親子そっくり}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...{紅緒さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My one and only Benio...{僕だけの紅緒さんたった一人の}
