Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Innen, watch your step!{印念中佐足元が}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I? I'm not drunk at all!{from the italian version}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to pay attention!{言わんこっちゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Lieutenant?{大丈夫でありますか中佐だろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type to collapse after that little alcohol,{あれぐらいの酒に足を取られるわしではない}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next bar!{次へ行こう}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to yer favourite place this time!{今度は貴様たちの行きつけの店はないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's do it.{ではこんなに申し上げます}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna ride that horse! Stop it!{わしも乗りたいあの馬止めろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance! It would be awful!{そんな無茶な因縁をつけろってんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Any problem?{ないいいね- has to be some wordplay}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Lieutenant Innen!{わしゃ印念中佐だぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Sublieutenant Ijuuin!{おあれは伊集院少尉殿です}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Ijuuin?{何伊集院}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublieutenant! Stop a second!{ちょっと止まれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yikes.{あーまずい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop there!{止まれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme that horse!{そのお任せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go!{よし行くぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad!{失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any respect!?{from italian}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How insolent!{無礼者}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn manners, {軍人は礼儀を正しく進め}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,did you forget military etiquette, you moron!?{軍人直営を忘れだかバカ者}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow...{ありゃありゃありゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't this where I got on the rickshaw?{さっき乗った場所じゃないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've only gone round and round from the very start!{さっきからぐるぐる堂々巡りしてるじゃないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!{だからよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya that I didn't wanna leave, didn't I?{このうちから離れたくねえんだって言ったろうが}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I get myself into?{[?]に乗っちゃったのー}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, perhaps because you grew up selfish, {とにかくお前はわがままに育ったせいか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have enough patience.{辛抱というものが足りんのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm patient enough.{いいえ、十分に辛抱しました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of man Mr. Ijuuin is,{たとえ伊集院君がどんな男であろうと}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,as a bride, you must dedicate him every ounce of patience.{嫁たるもの、忍の一字で尽くすものなのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The cigarettes "Golden Bat"{紙巻タバコのゴールデンバットは}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,were put on the market ten years prior, in 1906,{これより10年ほど前の明治39年に発売され}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and cost 4000 yen per pack.{10本で4000だった}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At home you obey your parents,{家にあっては親に従い、}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as a wife, you obey your husband,{嫁しては夫に従い、}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're old you obey your sons.{老いては子に従う}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how women and children in Japan{日本の婦女子たるものすべからく}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,have to behave.{こうであらねばならぬ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so antiquated, Father.{古い、古い、お父様}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to the mansion. Shinobu is probably worried about you.{りなさい、今頃伊集院君が心配しておるだろう……}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... anachronism isn't just a Ijuuin thing.{なんと時代錯誤は伊集院家だけじゃなかったのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, go back there!{Benio, 戻りなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you won't care no matter what happens to me, Father!?{じゃあお父様は、私がどんな目に遭っても構わないのね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a woman leaves a house,{女が一旦家を出たからには}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,she shall never return there!{この家の敷居を二度とまたいではならん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuses are futile!{くどい、弁解無用ぢゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.{わかりました}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go.{私出ていきます}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never come back!{二度と帰ってきません}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lady Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I knew you'd argue for a while,{今夜はたっぷりさかが続くと思って}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about making some noodles for dinner!{お夜食にそうめんでも茹でようかと支度してた ところなんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never taste your noodles again, Nanny.{ばあやのそうめん、二度と味わうこともないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?{どうしたんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I got kicked out. This time from my house.{追い出されたの、今度はこの家から}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?{なんですって}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a second!{ちょっと待ってくださいますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it always end up like this?{このうちの人はすぐこうなんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, don't be so hasty!{いいですか早まっちゃいけません}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear, I couldn't do otherwise.{母さんや[?]仕方なかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for her sake,{伊集院家返す}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to send her back to the Ijuuins'.{それがあの子のためだと思うんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, don't be so thoughtless!{旦那さま早まっちゃいけません}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Why are you upset?{何だってお前こそ何を早まっておるのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to commit suicide?{自害なさるとこじゃなかったんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm stupid?{バカを申すな}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a daughter like Benio,{紅緒のような娘を持ってみい}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how many times you kill yourself it won't be enough!{その度ごとに自害しておったんでは、命がいくつあっても足ぁりまいが}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.{それもそうですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How insulting! Alright, if it has to be this way...{なんたる侮辱よしこうなったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go away in no time!{絶対におん出ってやる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, please stop it...{お嬢様やめてくださいます}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, take care, nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Father, okay?{お父様のこと 頼むわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the worst.{最悪の実態}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Professor,{ねえねえ若師匠}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been a long time, huh?{本当久しぶりね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?{どこ行ってたんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the food is ready{さあお料理も揃ったし}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have already plans for the next spectacle,{来月のおさらい会の見通しもついたから}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,won't you take the lead for this toast, Professor?{ね若師匠乾杯の音頭をとってくださいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.\NThen,{いいわよそれじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to our health, to the Fujieda-style acting{皆さんの健康と藤枝流の俳優と}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and to the success of next month's spectacle.{来月のおさらい会の成功を祈って}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!{乾杯}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord!{大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!{大変なのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you such in a hurry, Nanny?{あれどうしたのばあやさんそんなに慌てて}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady has fled from the house once again!{お嬢様がまた家飛び出すのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop her, Ranmaru!{止めてranmaruさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful!{そりゃ大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go too!{私も行かなくっちゃあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, everyone, I'm leaving!{じゃあ皆さん失礼するわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?{ええ何ですって}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?{どこへ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't really know it either.{さあ私にもよくわからないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do with next month's show?{じゃ来月のおさらい会はどうするんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's not the time for that!{こっちはそれどころじゃないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I had already booked the theatre...{だって劇場にも予約したんだし}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had already ordered the costumes...{衣装の注文も出しちゃったし}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of this food, on top of it!{大地この料理はどうすんのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, see you, bye-bye!{それじゃねバイバイ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Professor...{ちょっと若師匠ったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at a loss...{俺だからもう}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny, what should we do?{ばあやどうしてくれるんだい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to disturb your plans,{私だってらんまるさんをけしかけに来たわけじゃないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to stop Benio.{止めてもらうつもりだったのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!{待って}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't take this anymore!{いやこんな生活耐えられない}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You only care about soldiers,{何さ軍人軍人と威張るなって}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever come back there,{二度と帰ってきてやんないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret you, stupid dad!{後悔するなよーくそ親父}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait! Then, let's go!{お待たせさ行きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady!{お嬢様}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone...{いっちまった}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi! This is bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it, Nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady and Ranmaru have fled, please stop them!{嬢様と蘭丸(???)飛び出す早く止めて}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll lend you a hand.{じゃあおいらもお供しなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, please get off the rickshaw,{お爺さん降りてくんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,now gimme my tip!{車チっと逆手早くよこせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me,{冗談じゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't move an inch ever since I got on this rickshaw,{私はここで乗り込んでからまだ一歩も前進してないんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what in the world would I pay you for!?{なんてとんでもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now shut up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord...{旦那様}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I might've gone a bit overboard.{わしも少し言い過ぎたかもしれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you reprimanded her too much,{薬が効きすぎたんでございますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but i know that it's hard to deal with her.{お嬢様にはさじ加減が難しいんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be happy if Benio returned home,{benioが帰ってきてくれてわしも嬉しかった が}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but after all I have no choice but{やはりあの子のためを思えば}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,make her come back to the Ijuuin mansion.{伊集院家に返しかあるまい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What could that be?{/can it be...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!{ごめんください}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's here after all!{やっぱり迎えに来たか}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Shinobu.{伊集院君か}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for intruding so late.{夜分失礼いたします}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Hanamura,{花村少佐殿}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry for what I've caused this time.{この度は自分が至らずに申し訳ないことをしました}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not only your fault.{いや君だけが悪いのではない}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio should be here...{紅生さんはおいででしょうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't she come back to your place yet?{紅緒はまだ君の家に戻っておらんのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I told her to come back there.{いやさっき君のところへ帰したとこだが}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have not arrived yet,{まだおつきになっていませんよきっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,she went out only a while ago, after all.{お出かけになったのほんの少し前ですもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look for her.{確かめてみます}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'll use your telephone.{すみません電話をお借りします}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I want to talk with the Ijuuin family in Otowadai.{もしもし、音羽台の伊集院家をお願いします}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ijuuin.{そうです、伊集院です}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss, this is the wrong way,{ね親分道はちがいやすぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't lead to the count's mansion.{こっち行ったんじゃ伯爵家は遠回りで}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who told you we'd go back there?{誰があの家戻るって言ったのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.{あそうじゃあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if Benio returns,{紅緒さんが戻られたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lead her to her room and make her rest.{部屋へ通してお休みになっていただくように}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back shortly. See you later.{僕もまもなく帰りますじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not home yet.{まだ帰ってないそうです}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry, it might be hard for her to show up after all of this.{いや心配はないあれのことだ 帰りにくくてその辺にいるのだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...{そうでしょうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll go home and look for her.{では心当たりを探しながら家に戻ることにします}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.{そうしてくれたまえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Sorry for the trouble.{はいご心配かけまして}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ijuuin.{伊集院君あ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Benio told me about{そのぉ、紅緒が言っておったのだが}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a geisha{柳橋の}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,from Yanagibashi or something.{芸者とか何とか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, about that thing,{そのことでしたら}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it's nothing you should worry about, Commander,{少佐がご心配になっているようなことでは ありません}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you can relax.{ご安心ください}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I trusted you all along.{そうだろうわしは君を信じておったのだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.{ありがとうございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio jumped to conclusions right away, so I didn't tell anything,{benioさんにも 話さなくて済むことならと思いまして黙ってたんですが}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to her about it when the time comes.{いつか折りを見て話すつもりです}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.{そうしてくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be leaving.{では失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ijuuin!{伊集院君}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of her.{あれをよろしく頼む}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she might be careless-{至らない娘だが}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!{とんでもありません}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is the kind of person{benioさんはやはり}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she would be,{自分が思ってた通りの方でした}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on the contrary, I think that I'm the one that's worthy of her.{かえって自分こそが紅緒さんにふさわしくあらねばと考えています}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ijuuin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio, what are we going to do?{ねぇBenioさんどうするの}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being loud. I'm thinking.{うるさいわね今考えてるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been thinking for a while, haven't you?{さっきからずっと考えてるじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm out of both houses now, you know,{だって両方の家を自分からおんでてきたんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't come back to neither.{どっちも戻れないでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After saying those things,{あんなこと言って出てきて}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's too late to come back home.{今更家には帰れないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, I would never return to the mansion.{かといって伊集院家に戻るなんてまっぴらだし}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it always end up like this?{私ってどうしていつもこうなのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of it.{自分で嫌なっちゃうわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, Boss Benio,{えbenio親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how about, on this occasion,{どうですこの際}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we drink something and paaarty hard?{酒でも飲んでパーっとうざばらしなんてな}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! That'd be a great idea!{そうねそれも良いわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I might try hot sake this time too!{この際焼けサクの味も覚えておこうかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, no!{ダメだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that Benio can't hold alcohol!{Benioさん酒乱んなんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can go home on your own.{じゃああんただけ一人で言えよ帰り}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with your rudeness!{意地悪もういいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, let's go!{Ushigorou, さ 行きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Lessgo, lessgo! \NC'mon, Ushigoro, lessgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudeness, rudeness, why is everyone so rude to me?{意地悪意地悪僕いつも知ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you company!{私がついてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Shinobu? That womaniser...{少尉が何するあの女たらし}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it, Father was on his side.{おまけにお父様も少尉の方をもつし}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking bring so much joy! Let's get fired up!{飲むこと全て喜びだはぁドンと持ってこい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.{はいお待ちどうさま}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one!{じゃんじゃん行こう}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, Boss!{さすが親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi! Don't make her drink any more!{うしさんべにおさんに飲ませるはいい加減にして}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,alcohol is the right cure!{from italian}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw Shinobu, screw Father,{少尉がなんら、おやじがなんら}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,screw soldiers, dammit!{軍人がなんらってんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How annoying.{うるさいなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant, let's leave.{中佐殿もうおひらきですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say nonsense, we've just started, I'm just a bit tipsy.{バカ言うなこれからだちょっと酔ったしい}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!{ちょっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell you doin'!?{なにすんですかっ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat on something.{何か踏んづけたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My hat!{ワシの帽子}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! How dare you do this to a soldier?{貴様軍人の被り物なんたる無礼な}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier? You think I care?{軍人？軍人がどうしたのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Her eyes are glazed!{目が据ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin's a soldier, Father's a soldier,{伊集院も軍人、お父様も軍人}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,this disgusting guy's a soldier too!{このやらしい男も軍人}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch, respect imperial soldiers!{己、帝国軍人に向かって}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this?{何よこんなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!{はいいちにのよいと}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your sword? It's nothing special.{こんななまくら差してるようじゃ大したことないわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious saber...{わしの大切なサーベルが。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers, soldiers,{軍人軍人って}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,stop boasting that!{威張るんじゃないだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our high collar lady is furious,{およしあそばせはいからさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but she chose a risky opponent.{今夜の相手は悪かった}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is Shinobu's direct superior{この男こそ伊集院少尉の運命を}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and is like a devil that can control his future.{言って握る悪魔のような直属上端だったの だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, she has no clue.{知らぬが仏と言いますな}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's for sure is that her future{一寸先は夜の闇}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is black as the darkest night!{はいからさんの(?)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The imperial army is no match{帝国陸軍何するものと}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for the drunken blooming Benio,{酒乱の花が乱れ咲き}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as she stands up against five men.{5人相手におおたちまわり}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio keeps fighting and Ushigorou calls for reinforcements,{親分早押しushigorouは援軍迎えに走ったが}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.93,0:23:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but Shinobu is nowhere to be seen,{少尉はおらず行き違い}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.02,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,while the count comes across the situation!{変わって老伯爵が旗名枠が[?] }
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio's surely incurred a lot of grudge!{たっぷり恨みを買いました}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time in Here Comes the High Collar Lady:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Incurring grudge is dangerous!{恨み買いますご用心} \NDon't miss it!
